Description.Desc:
Hold <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Unleash a charged slash forward, dealing massive <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
When Xiao'Zhao triggers <color=#FFFFFF>[Quick Assist]</color> during a skill and is switched out, automatically transitions into <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Charged Slash]</color> and begins charging;
While charging, Xiao'Zhao accumulates up to 5s of charge time. The next time <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Charged Slash]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[Chain Attack]</color>, or <color=#FFFFFF>[Assist Follow-Up]</color> deals DMG, it will consume the charge time to deal additional DMG, dealing {CAL:0.12+AvatarSkillLevel(0)*0.01,100,2}% of Xiao'Zhao's max HP as additional DMG for every 1s of charge time.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Evade> to activate:
A quick dash dodge;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Special> to activate:
Slash enemies in front, dealing <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, if Xiao'Zhao's current HP is above 50%, consumes 6% of max HP to restore HP to all squad members based on 1% of Xiao'Zhao's max HP per second for 5 seconds. This effect can trigger once every 15 seconds.

With enough energy, press <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady> to activate:
Slash forward at enemies, dealing massive <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, if Xiao'Zhao's current HP is above 50%, consumes 6% of max HP to restore HP for all squad members based on 1% of Xiao'Zhao's max HP per second for 5 seconds. This effect can trigger once every 15 seconds;
Upon activating this skill, grants the whole squad a <color=#FFFFFF>[Boost]</color> effect. When triggered under <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Health]</color>, activates <color=#FFFFFF>[Quick Assist]</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When a <color=#FFFFFF>Chain Attack</color> is triggered, select the character to activate:
Dealing massive <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, accumulate 15 [Ice Point];
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When Decibel Rating is at <color=#FFFFFF>Maximum</color>, press <IconMap:Icon_UltimateReady> to activate:
Forward attack followed by a falling slash on enemies, dealing massive <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
Upon activating this skill, accumulate 20 [Ice Point];
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

When Xiao'Zhao's [Ice Point] gauge is full, press <IconMap:Icon_Switch> to activate:
Dealing massive <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
When Xiao'Zhao triggers <color=#FFFFFF>[Quick Assist]</color> during a skill and is switched out, automatically chains into <color=#FFFFFF>[Basic Attack: Charged Slash]</color> and begins charging;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>[Defensive Assist]</color> to activate:
Deals massive <color=#98EFF0>Ice DMG</color>;
After activation, if <color=#FFFFFF>[Ice Point]</color> gauge is full, press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to chain into an <color=#FFFFFF>[Entry Skill]</color>;
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Desc:
Xiao'Zhao gains additional CRIT Rate based on initial Max HP, increasing CRIT Rate by 0.8% for every 1000 Max HP;
When on-field Agents deal DMG, Daze enemies, or defeat enemies, Xiao'Zhao accumulates 1.5/15/10 [Ice Point] respectively, triggering at most once every 1/50/50 seconds, up to 100;
When [Ice Point] is full, switching Xiao'Zhao to on-field position activates <color=#FFFFFF>[Entry Skill]</color>;
When Xiao'Zhao activates <color=#FFFFFF>[Entry Skill]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Health]</color> is activated for 50 seconds. When triggered again, the existing <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Health]</color> will be deactivated;
When Xiao'Zhao activates <color=#FFFFFF>[EX Special Attack]</color> or <color=#FFFFFF>[Entry Skill]</color>, the Brigade gains <color=#FFFFFF>[Boost]</color> effect, increasing ATK by 100 for 40 seconds. Repeated triggers extend the duration. When this effect triggers under <color=#FFFFFF>[Ether Veil: Health]</color>, <color=#FFFFFF>[Quick Assist]</color> will be activated.

